title: Catalan separatists expected to hold mass independence rally
description:
Subscribe to France 24 now:
http://f24.my/youtubeEN

FRANCE 24 live news stream: all the latest news 24/7
http://f24.my/YTliveEN

Hundreds of thousands of people in Catalonia are set to take to the streets for the region's day, which marks the fall of Barcelona to Madrid three centuries ago. The day has long been used by separatists to promote their cause. This, one year after Catalonia declared independence from Spain.
